<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="bn">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>অনলাইন লাইব্রেরি | রূপগঞ্জ পশ্চিম</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Hind+Siliguri:wght@300;400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-green: #008144;
            --dark-bg: #0a0f0d;
            --footer-bg: #051a0f;
            --glass-white: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            --glass-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
            --accent-yellow: #ffb700;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Hind Siliguri', sans-serif;
            background: radial-gradient(circle at top left, #071d11, #081110 65%);
            color: #edf2f7;
            min-height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
        }

        .content { max-width: 1140px; margin: 30px auto; padding: 0 18px; }
        .card-grid { display: grid; gap: 20px; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr)); }
        .lib-card {
            background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 24px;
            transition: transform 0.25s ease, border-color 0.25s ease;
        }
        .lib-card:hover { transform: translateY(-4px); border-color: #84cc16; }
        .lib-card h4 { margin-bottom: 12px; font-size: 1.05rem; }
        .lib-card p { color: #cbd5e1; font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.6; }
        .lib-card a { display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; margin-top: 16px; color: #d9f99d; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 600; }
        .lib-card a:hover { color: #bef264; }
        .badge-type { font-size: 0.8rem; padding: 5px 10px; border-radius: 999px; background: rgba(255,255,255,0.08); color: #d1fae5; }
        .empty-state { color: #94a3b8; font-size: 1rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/main-nav') %>

    <main class="content">
        <section class="mb-4">
            <div class="d-flex flex-column flex-md-row justify-content-between align-items-start gap-3">
                <div>
                    <h2 class="fw-bold">লাইব্রেরি সামগ্রী</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted">নিচের আছে বই, ডকুমেন্ট ও পড়ার লিঙ্ক। ছবি বা বই পড়ুন এ ক্লিক করলে সরাসরি সেটি খুলবে।</p>
                </div>
                <a href="/admin" class="btn btn-outline-success btn-sm">অ্যাডমিন প্যানেলে যান</a>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="card-grid">
            <% if (resources && resources.length > 0) { %>
                <% resources.forEach(resource => { %>
                    <article class="lib-card">
                        <% if (resource.imageUrl) { %>
                            <a href="<%= resource.url %>" target="_blank" style="display: block; overflow: hidden; border-radius: 10px; margin-bottom: 12px;">
                                <img src="<%= resource.imageUrl %>" alt="<%= resource.title %>" style="width: 100%; height: 200px; object-fit: cover; transition: 0.3s;" />
                            </a>
                        <% } %>
                        <span class="badge-type"><%= resource.visibility %></span>
                        <h4><%= resource.title %></h4>
                        <% if (resource.imageUrl) { %>
                            <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; color: #a0a0a0;">বইয়ের কভার দেখুন এবং পড়ুন</p>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <p><%= resource.url %></p>
                        <% } %>
                        <a href="<%= resource.url %>" target="_blank"><i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i> বই পড়ুন বা লিঙ্ক খুলুন</a>
                    </article>
                <% }) %>
            <% } else { %>
                <div class="empty-state">কোনো পাবলিক লাইব্রেরি লিঙ্ক পাওয়া যায়নি।</div>
            <% } %>
        </section>
    </main>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>